{"tid":1550052,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act」｜ 香港人最愛嘅懶人包出現啦","createTime":"2019-09-07T14:05:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T01:17:39.000Z","uid":286309,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c492e52639cccfe9781dd2bf4b7e97de9ae87c8a","tid":1550052,"uid":286309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:05:53.000Z","msg":"到現家仲未熟人權法案嘅，睇撚埋條片佢。 <br />\n唔想聽日個個變藍絲癈老，聽日人地問你&quot;What is the act about ?&quot;，你就 &quot;Er...er...er&quot; <br />\n唔準Er 要好自信答佢 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">&quot; Hongkonger want the act pass!&quot;</span></span><br />\n<br />\n提提大家，我地聽日係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請願</span></span> 唔撚係示威，唔撚係示威 唔撚係示威    <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有唔好射美領，要聽日完左之後美領完好無缺 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">天佑香港，還我普選</span></strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FizKlXXncH8&amp;t=0s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFizKlXXncH8%26t%3D0s&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQCwEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=7bf6236a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FizKlXXncH8&amp;t=0s</a> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">香港人權與民主法案祈禱會<br />\n日期：9月8日（星期日）<br />\n【遮打花園集會】<br />\n時間：下午1時30分至6時30分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n【流水式自發到美領館】<br />\n時間：下午2時起<br />\n地點：美國駐港澳總領事館<br />\n主辦：民間發起 </span>"},{"pid":"dad8d89c94de72da35a411924aee83319457c483","tid":1550052,"uid":9640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0